OL,3,C'Raging' drug user who murdered ex-
OL,4,Csoldier in 'cruel' attack jailed
OL,6,FA 32-year-old man has been jailed for
OL,7,Flife for the murder of an Iraq War
OL,8,Fveteran who he punched three times in
OL,9,Fa drink and drug-fuelled street attack
OL,10,Fwhich led to his death 10 months later.
OL,12,FGregory Twigg was sentenced to a
OL,13,Fminimum term of 11 years after a court
OL,14,Fheard how he landed the "powerful and
OL,15,Fcowardly" punches on medically-retired
OL,16,FBritish Army veteran Lee Woodward in
OL,17,FStoke-on-Trent, Staffordshire.
