OL,3,C'Raging' drug user who murdered ex-
OL,4,Csoldier in 'cruel' attack jailed
OL,6,FThe attack on the night of June 24
OL,7,F2022 left the former soldier severely
OL,8,Fbrain damaged and he died in hospital
OL,9,Fon April 26 2023.
OL,11,FTwigg, who was already serving an
OL,12,Feight-year and three-month prison
OL,13,Fsentence after pleading guilty in
OL,14,FSeptember 2022 to grievous bodily harm
OL,15,Fwith intent, was found guilty of
OL,16,Fmurder by jurors at a second trial
OL,17,Fwhich ended in July this year.
