OL,6,FAt his sentencing hearing Twigg was
OL,7,Fcriticised by the judge for "stringing
OL,8,Fout" the case by pleading not guilty
OL,9,Fto murder, extending and amplifying
OL,10,Fthe anguish of his victim's partner
OL,11,Fand stepdaughters.
OL,13,FIn victim impact statements read to
OL,14,Fthe court on Friday, relatives of the
OL,15,F39-year-old victim described their
OL,16,Ffeelings of pain and anguish during Mr
OL,17,FWoodward's "deterioration" in hospital.
OL,19,FMr Woodward was someone who kept his
OL,20,Ffamily strong, they said.
