OL,6,FThe trial was told Mr Woodward had
OL,7,Fbeen on a night out with his fiancee
OL,8,FKate Griffin, and had left The Liquor
OL,9,FVaults pub in Trade Street minutes
OL,10,Fbefore her, when he became involved in
OL,11,Fa confrontation with the occupants of
OL,12,Fa Vauxhall Astra that had been driving
OL,13,Fpast him.
OL,15,FIn her victim impact statement to the
OL,16,Fcourt, Ms Griffin said: "My boy and us
OL,17,Fas a family went through hell."
