OL,6,FShe added that the injuries caused to
OL,7,Fher partner had been "severe and
OL,8,Fcruel" and watching his condition
OL,9,Fworsen in hospital had been
OL,10,F"absolutely horrific".
OL,12,FTwigg, who admitted he had taken
OL,13,Fcocaine and had drunk vodka and
OL,14,Fsambuca, told his trial he had become
OL,15,Fangry after Mr Woodward had allegedly
OL,16,Fsworn at and threatened him and his
OL,17,Ffriends as they were driving past him
OL,18,Fon their way to a night out.
