OL,6,FProsecution counsel David Mason KC
OL,7,Fsaid Twigg was "fired up on drink and
OL,8,Fcoke and raging" when he attacked Mr
OL,9,FWoodward, who he said posed no threat
OL,10,Fto the defendant, after the first
OL,11,Fpunch left him looking "like a highly
OL,12,Fdazed boxer".
OL,14,FCCTV showed Twigg knocking Mr
OL,15,FWoodward, who was over 6ft, to the
OL,16,Fground, before a second punch knocked
OL,17,Fhim into a parked car.
