OL,6,FA third punch delivered 32 seconds
OL,7,Flater left the victim unconscious in
OL,8,Fthe road and Twigg fled the scene with
OL,9,Fhis friends.
OL,11,FHe was arrested less than an hour
OL,12,Flater in Newcastle-under-Lyme.
OL,14,FTwigg told the jury he never intended
OL,15,Fto cause Mr Woodward serious harm and
OL,16,Fhad only wanted to give him a black
OL,17,Feye so that he would leave him and his
OL,18,Ffriends alone.
