OL,6,FHe said he punched him twice more
OL,7,Fbecause he feared Mr Woodward was
OL,8,Fgoing to hit him back, and he was
OL,9,F"devastated" that his actions had
OL,10,Fresulted in his death.
OL,12,FIt emerged in court that Twigg has
OL,13,Fthree previous convictions for battery
OL,14,Fbetween 2014 and 2019 and was jailed
OL,15,Ffor 30 months in 2020 for making
OL,16,Fthreats to kill and burglary.
