OL,6,FDefence KC Ahmed Hossain told the
OL,7,Fcourt in mitigation: "Mr Twigg readily
OL,8,Funderstands that he is going to
OL,9,Freceive a life sentence and offers
OL,10,Fremorse.
OL,12,F"He now understands not just the
OL,13,Fdreadful and tragic outcome of his
OL,14,Fviolence but he also understands some
OL,15,Fof the triggers of that violence."
OL,17,FPassing sentence on Twigg, formerly of
OL,18,FBlurton, Stoke-on-Trent, Judge Roger
OL,19,FThomas KC ruled that the minimum term
OL,20,Fto be served from the point of
OL,21,Fsentencing would be 11 years.
