OL,6,FThe judge said the minimum term would
OL,7,Fhave been 14 years, but time served
OL,8,Fand spent on remand meant it had to be
OL,9,Freduced by three years.
OL,11,FThe judge told Twigg: "Although you
OL,12,Fmay regret the consequences of your
OL,13,Funlawful violence in so far as the
OL,14,Fconsequences are concerned for you, it
OL,15,Fis difficult to accept that you are
OL,16,Ftruly remorseful in any wider sense."
