OL,9,Fcarried out in three stages, the judge
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FSpeaking in July after the four-day
OL,13,Fmurder trial, Detective Sergeant Garry
OL,14,FJackson said: "This is an extremely
OL,15,Ftragic case that has caused
OL,16,Fimmeasurable pain and loss to Lee's
OL,17,Ffamily.
